comments: Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) off-arm that does not affect his SQBR.
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes marginal contact to Lillard's (POR) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Covington (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Covington (POR) lowers his arm and makes contact to Porzingis' (DAL) arm during his shot attempt near the basket.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) arm on the drive that affects his control of the ball.
Lillard (POR) attempts to deflect the ball and brushes Doncic's (DAL) arm during his drive.
Porzingis (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Covington (POR) and absorbs the contact.
Covington (POR) reaches in during Doncic's (DAL) drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs as he finishes at the rim.
Doncic (DAL) is positioned in Anthony's (POR) space and marginal contact occurs as Anthony begins to face up.
Porzingis (DAL) makes incidental contact with Jones Jr.'s (POR) body after the release of his shot attempt at the basket.
Brunson (DAL) cleanly dislodges the ball from Trent Jr. (POR) and is last to make contact with the ball prior to it going out of bounds.
